      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>A swirl or black and gray shadows is suspended in this cool, clear fluid. When you drink a shadowfilm serum, your eyes (or equivalent visual organs) become coated with a film of shadow that protects your eyes from bright light and harmful effects. For 1 hour after you drink this serum, you treat light levels of bright light as normal light. Additionally, you gain a +4 circumstance bonus to saving throws against effects that inflict the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.tOpF6qjnlnKc10t7]{blinded} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.YjE6UGzwOTfO9p4g]{dazzled} conditions. If you fail a save against an effect that would cause you to become blinded, you become dazzled instead.</p>"
    },
